801, 190.6371, 190.9309, 192.3847, 192.1644, 193.1033, 193.3223, 192.9824, 192.5548, 193.3339, 194.7043, 192.9706, 194.2061, 194.2261, 193.5102, 193.2358, 195.9514, 196.3692, 198.3509, 197.4656, 197.6823, 197.9825, 198.2702, 199.9716, 198.6115, 199.8127, 200.1565, 199.473, 200.8358, 201.0452, 202.6931, 202.8778, 203.7584, 203.4782, 204.2202, 202.0105, 201.0398, 202.8217, 203.4604, 203.0522, 202.3833, 202.7135, 203.9691, 202.588, 202.5353, 203.2228, 201.9861, 201.8371, 202.0906, 201.6522, 202.888, 202.4127, 200.9807, 201.2378, 201.9423, 201.5791, 201.3079, 200.5254, 201.6798, 201.3129, 201.0768, 201.1316, 201.5252, 201.248, 199.9445, 201.9982, 203.4829, 203.8046, 202.4477, 204.8794, 202.1735, 202.3073, 201.6168, 200.6766, 199.4812, 199.5823, 198.5415, 200.3135, 200.0938, 198.3198, 197.4774, 194.6038, 195.0761, 193.7802, 193.7198, 193.4519, 193.3463, 193.9634, 194.7734, 194.6407, 195.4523, 196.6183, 197.1843, 197.9917, 198.3772, 198.6903, 198.4741, 197.9008, 198.7638, 198.7919, 198.7982, 198.3063, 198.926, 198.6281, 199.3782, 198.8532, 198.7742, 200.0301, 200.5583, 199.406, 199.1295, 201.4179, 200.2077, 200.7178, 200.9175, 202.4422, 202.4781, 205.2274, 204.1659, 204.1959, 202.6654, 204.8098, 205.8022, 206.7006, 206.8538, 206.075, 206.1412, 207.1199, 207.0051, 208.4994, 209.3632, 210.2312, 210.2372, 211.105, 211.2532, 210.7781, 209.6779, 210.2174, 211.7454, 214.2281, 215.604, 216.2526, 218.0047, 217.0661, 217.4904, 217.9104, 221.0394, 219.965, 220.4288, 220.4068, 221.2409, 221.8356, 220.7758, 222.3712, 221.4198, 220.993, 221.2489, 221.3148, 220.988, 220.0232, 219.7096, 221.0617, 222.7044, 222.8403, 221.3991, 220.0357, 221.2031, 220.6837, 221.4473, 222.6302, 222.4109, 225.0638, 226.4358, 225.7935, 224.655, 223.4022, 222.2605, 221.4288, 221.3521, 221.6179, 222.5154, 221.348, 222.5343, 223.8981, 223.73, 224.1605, 223.4355, 224.4142, 226.3531, 226.5804, 228.1287, 228.8646, 230.6422, 228.9921, 229.3484, 229.5763, 228.5399, 225.6993, 225.7117, 227.0834, 227.5788, 228.1512, 227.7722, 229.0487, 229.7017, 228.9509, 232.7944, 233.9904, 232.7419, 232.0277, 232.9877, 238.8243, 242.6032, 241.6029, 241.8799, 243.6331, 244.3626, 243.9458, 245.5378, 244.325, 245.5219, 245.6112, 246.3184, 246.2844, 248.2186, 246.6057, 246.1503, 245.759, 245.6052, 247.2673, 247.4109, 245.4518, 245.8168, 245.4433], "summary_html": "<h1>商品多因子模型研究框架初探</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本研报系统梳理了商品期货多因子模型的研究框架，覆盖7大类因子：动量、期限结构、库存、套保压力、持仓、波动率、流动性。R1-R3 聚焦于期限结构（basis）因子，R4-R5 专攻持仓/库存/流动性等非carry维度的修正与优化。</p>\n<p><strong>核心发现</strong>：库存因子的方向纠正和窗口拉长是本次迭代的关键突破。原始实现中库存变化率为正=库存增加=做多，但正确的经济逻辑是低库存=供给紧缺=看涨。将库存因子翻转方向并改用252日z-score后，Sharpe从-0.57跃升至1.37，同时会员持仓因子也从-0.44改善至+0.41。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.38</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>5.5%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.0%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-7.1%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.04</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>2947</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.37</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>2.87</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.33 / 1.42</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.49</td><td>0.09</td><td>1.59</td><td>1.03</td><td>0.36</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.83</span></td><td>1.41</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.06</span></td><td>1.63</td><td>0.73</td><td>0.79</td><td>1.1</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">5.17</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>inventory_21</code></td><td>库存(21日)</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 10 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 10 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>58</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>2949</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>97.5%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>32.5</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<h3>核心因子（负库存z-score）</h3>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{inv\\_neg}_{i,t} = -\\frac{\\ln(\\text{inv}_{i,t}) - \\mu_{i,t}^{252}}{\\sigma_{i,t}^{252}}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\mu_{i,t}^{252}</span> 和 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma_{i,t}^{252}</span> 是品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 过去252个交易日库存对数值的滚动均值和标准差。负号确保低库存品种获得高因子值。</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_i = \\text{rank}(\\text{inv\\_neg}_i) \\in [0, 1]</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_i = (\\text{rank}_i - 0.5) \\times 2 \\times \\frac{\\sigma_{\\text{target}}}{\\hat{\\sigma}_i}</div>\n<h3>会员持仓因子（修正版）</h3>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{memb\\_lvl}_{i,t} = \\frac{\\text{memberdiff20}_{i,t}}{\\text{OI}_{i,t}}</div>\n<p>前20名会员净多空差占总持仓比例。正值=多头占优=看涨信号。</p>\n<h3>基本面组合</h3>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{fundE} = \\frac{1}{3}\\left(\\text{rank}(\\text{inv\\_neg252}) + \\text{rank}(\\text{basis}) + \\text{rank}(\\text{ry})\\right)</div>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>basis因子0.79, 换手率1.03过高</td><td>增加basis hold=20, carry组合</td><td><strong>basis20=0.83 突破0.8</strong>, 换手降至0.45</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>触发CS/TS归一化</td><td>自动添加_cs/_ts变体(63个)</td><td>未超越raw, basis20仍最优0.83</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>3轮最低要求达标</td><td>维持不变</td><td>decision=skip</td></tr><tr><td>R4</td><td>持仓/库存/流动性因子全部负Sharpe</td><td><strong>方向修正</strong>: inv取负(低库存=bullish), memb_lvl用水平而非变化率, Amihud取负</td><td>inv_neg: -0.57-&gt;+0.58, memb_lvl: -0.44-&gt;+0.41, fundcombo=0.60</td></tr><tr><td>R5</td><td>inv_neg最优0.58, 需扩大参数网格</td><td>252日窗口z-score + 多持仓期网格 + 基本面组合</td><td><strong>inv_neg252_10=1.37</strong>, 突破性提升</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折点</strong>: 1. R1: hold_days从5增至20，通过降低换手率使basis因子突破0.8 2. R4: 发现库存、会员持仓因子<strong>方向完全反了</strong>。库存增加应看空而非看多，memberdiff20水平值而非变化率才有经济含义 3. R5: 库存z-score窗口从60日拉长至252日，从0.58跳至1.37。年度窗口捕捉库存季节性周期，远优于短期噪声</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种（56个有库存数据的商品期货）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 10天再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>核心数据</strong>: <code>inventory_21</code>（库存21日口径，非空率约71%）</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 与因子库 <code>20141201_tianfeng_inv21_zs252_h42_raw</code> (Sharpe 1.54) 相关性0.75，verdict为 <code>likely_redundant</code> -- 本质上是同一因子逻辑（库存z-score，252日窗口）\n<p>- 2023年和2025年Sharpe接近0，库存因子在商品市场平静期效果偏弱 - 库存数据非空率71%，部分品种（如金融期货）无库存数据</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>K</code></td><td><code>20</code></td><td>base lookback (unused for inv_neg252 but kept for context)</td></tr><tr><td><code>INV_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>252</code></td><td>inventory z-score window</td></tr><tr><td><code>INV_MIN_PERIODS</code></td><td><code>84</code></td><td>max(252 // 3, 10)</td></tr><tr><td><code>SCALE</code></td><td><code>2.0</code></td><td>rank_to_continuous scale</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.18s</li>\n</ul>"}